    "{\n",
    " \"cells\": [\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"markdown\",\"metadata\":{},\"source\":[\"# Language Detection System\\n\",\"**NLP Project 18 of 100**\\n\",\"\\n\",\"## Project Overview\\n\",\"Build a system that detects the language of short text snippets. Compare character n-gram features with the `langdetect` library.\\n\",\"\\n\",\"## Learning Objectives\\n\",\"1. Use character n-grams for language identification.\\n\",\"2. Compare custom ML models with off-the-shelf libraries.\\n\",\"3. Handle multilingual text in NLP pipelines.\\n\",\"\\n\",\"## Problem Statement\\n\",\"Given a text snippet, predict its language. Essential for multilingual NLP routing.\\n\",\"\\n\",\"## Why This Matters\\n\",\"- Multilingual platforms need to detect language before processing.\\n\",\"- Wrong language routing causes pipeline failures.\\n\",\"- Short texts (tweets, queries) are harder to classify.\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"markdown\",\"metadata\":{},\"source\":[\"## Dataset: Synthetic multilingual samples.\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"code\",\"execution_count\":null,\"metadata\":{},\"outputs\":[],\"source\":[\"import subprocess, sys, importlib\\nfor pkg in [\\\"pandas\\\",\\\"numpy\\\",\\\"matplotlib\\\",\\\"seaborn\\\",\\\"scikit-learn\\\",\\\"langdetect\\\"]:\\n    try: importlib.import_module(pkg)\\n    except ImportError: subprocess.check_call([sys.executable,\\\"-m\\\",\\\"pip\\\",\\\"install\\\",\\\"-q\\\",pkg])\\nprint('Ready.')\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"code\",\"execution_count\":null,\"metadata\":{},\"outputs\":[],\"source\":[\"import numpy as np, pandas as pd, matplotlib.pyplot as plt, seaborn as sns\\nimport warnings; warnings.filterwarnings('ignore')\\nsns.set_style('whitegrid')\\n%matplotlib inline\\nfrom sklearn.feature_extraction.text import TfidfVectorizer\\nfrom sklearn.linear_model import LogisticRegression\\nfrom sklearn.metrics import accuracy_score, classification_report, confusion_matrix\\nfrom sklearn.model_selection import train_test_split\\nprint('Loaded.')\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"code\",\"execution_count\":null,\"metadata\":{},\"outputs\":[],\"source\":[\"SEED = 42; np.random.seed(SEED); rng = np.random.default_rng(SEED)\\n\\nsamples = {\\n    'English': ['The weather is nice today','Machine learning is fascinating','I love reading books','The stock market crashed yesterday','Python is a great programming language'] * 40,\\n    'Spanish': ['El clima es agradable hoy','Me encanta leer libros','La bolsa de valores cayó ayer','Python es un gran lenguaje','El aprendizaje automático es fascinante'] * 40,\\n    'French': ['Le temps est beau aujourd\\\\'hui','J\\\\'adore lire des livres','La bourse a chuté hier','Python est un excellent langage','L\\\\'apprentissage automatique est fascinant'] * 40,\\n    'German': ['Das Wetter ist heute schön','Ich liebe es Bücher zu lesen','Die Börse ist gestern gefallen','Python ist eine großartige Sprache','Maschinelles Lernen ist faszinierend'] * 40,\\n    'Italian': ['Il tempo è bello oggi','Mi piace leggere libri','La borsa è crollata ieri','Python è un ottimo linguaggio','L\\\\'apprendimento automatico è affascinante'] * 40,\\n}\\n\\nrows = []\\nfor lang, texts in samples.items():\\n    for t in texts:\\n        rows.append({'text': t, 'language': lang})\\n\\ndf = pd.DataFrame(rows).sample(frac=1, random_state=SEED).reset_index(drop=True)\\nprint(f'Shape: {df.shape}'); print(df['language'].value_counts()); df.head()\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"markdown\",\"metadata\":{},\"source\":[\"## Custom Model: Character N-gram + LogReg\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"code\",\"execution_count\":null,\"metadata\":{},\"outputs\":[],\"source\":[\"X_train, X_test, y_train, y_test = train_test_split(df['text'], df['language'], test_size=0.2, random_state=SEED)\\n\\ntfidf = TfidfVectorizer(analyzer='char_wb', ngram_range=(2,4), max_features=5000)\\nX_tr = tfidf.fit_transform(X_train); X_te = tfidf.transform(X_test)\\n\\nlr = LogisticRegression(max_iter=500, random_state=SEED)\\nlr.fit(X_tr, y_train)\\ny_pred = lr.predict(X_te)\\n\\nprint('=== Character N-gram + LogReg ===')\\nprint(f'Accuracy: {accuracy_score(y_test, y_pred):.4f}')\\nprint(classification_report(y_test, y_pred))\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"markdown\",\"metadata\":{},\"source\":[\"## Comparison: langdetect library\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"code\",\"execution_count\":null,\"metadata\":{},\"outputs\":[],\"source\":[\"from langdetect import detect\\nlang_map = {'en':'English','es':'Spanish','fr':'French','de':'German','it':'Italian'}\\n\\ny_pred_lib = []\\nfor t in X_test:\\n    try:\\n        detected = detect(t)\\n        y_pred_lib.append(lang_map.get(detected, 'Unknown'))\\n    except: y_pred_lib.append('Unknown')\\n\\nvalid = [i for i,(a,b) in enumerate(zip(y_test.values,y_pred_lib)) if b != 'Unknown']\\nacc_lib = accuracy_score([y_test.values[i] for i in valid], [y_pred_lib[i] for i in valid])\\nprint(f'langdetect accuracy: {acc_lib:.4f} ({len(valid)}/{len(y_test)} detected)')\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"code\",\"execution_count\":null,\"metadata\":{},\"outputs\":[],\"source\":[\"cm = confusion_matrix(y_test, y_pred, labels=sorted(df['language'].unique()))\\nplt.figure(figsize=(7,5))\\nsns.heatmap(cm, annot=True, fmt='d', cmap='Blues', xticklabels=sorted(df['language'].unique()), yticklabels=sorted(df['language'].unique()))\\nplt.title('Language Detection — Confusion Matrix'); plt.tight_layout(); plt.show()\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"markdown\",\"metadata\":{},\"source\":[\"## Summary\\n\",\"- **Character n-grams are very effective** for language detection (languages have distinct character patterns).\\n\",\"- **langdetect works well for longer texts** but struggles with very short snippets.\\n\",\"- **Custom models give more control** over language coverage and confidence thresholds.\\n\",\"- **This module is essential** as a preprocessing step for multilingual NLP pipelines.\"]}\n",
    " ],\n",
    " \"metadata\":{\"kernelspec\":{\"display_name\":\"Python 3\",\"language\":\"python\",\"name\":\"python3\"},\"language_info\":{\"name\":\"python\",\"version\":\"3.11.0\"}},\n",
    " \"nbformat\":4,\"nbformat_minor\":5\n",
    "}\n"
